Package: junctions
Type: Package
Title: Extend the Theory of Junctions
Version: 0.1
Date: 2017-11-07
Author: Thijs Janzen
Maintainer: Thijs Janzen <thijsjanzen@gmail.com>
URL: https//github.com/thijsjanzen/junctions
Description: Individual based simulations of hybridizating populations, where the accumulation of junctions is tracked. Furthermore, mathematical equations are provided to verify simulation outcomes.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.13)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++11
Suggests: testit, testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
